channel.description:
[size=18pt][b]EDIT: FIXED, I HAD BACKUP FILES AND I JUST REPLACED THE CACHE! MAKE SURE YOU ALWAYS BACKUP YOUR FILES!!![/b][/size]
Hello all, I added the Naval Models to my client, and the ints, I did add models in my client and for somereason this happend
[IMG]http://i302.photobucket.com/albums/nn119/PhotoCrazzy/GuyError.png[/img]
I delted the models and ints and re compiled my client I still have the same things, Even some of my NPCS are Like this please help!!!
Regards Dhfhy1
[size=18pt][b]EDIT: FIXED, I HAD BACKUP FILES AND I JUST REPLACED THE CACHE! MAKE SURE YOU ALWAYS BACKUP YOUR FILES!!![/b][/size]
